{"tid":1845023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆更大更陰森既政治盤算","createTime":"2020-01-27T02:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T08:36:45.000Z","uid":240968,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f437b15033c56a1244d3dcaa1550574dfba06065","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"香港人禁黑佢憎，<br />\n淋病月娥當然想香港人死清光<br />\n<br />\n但小弟係到諗，特區拒絕封關仲有d 咩動機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以㭍婆禁鬼小氣性格，最上心一定係落佢面，搞到全身蟻既反送中政治風波。個時屌到柒婆最應既係香港人同埋.....<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外國</span></span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">細絲驚恐</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算中國武漢病毒真係蝙蝠傳比人類，而非病毒研究外洩，只要唔封關，靠住湧緊落黎既大陸人，同航空/貨櫃樞紐，香港一日唔封關，一日都有大量病毒載體四處出航，遊走他國。屆時，香港將會係全世界<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肺炎病毒輸出城市之首</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換句話說，唔封關，柒婆就可以用武漢肺炎去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懲罰全世界</span></span></strong>，特別撐香港人，落過佢面既國家<br />\n<br />\n㭍婆將會係武漢肺炎事件，第一個明顯有心使用疫病作自己政治盤算既人。再誇張d 講句，林鄭月娥係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用緊生化武器</span></span></strong>，令更多人感染死亡。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 染婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港罷工 刻不容緩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faf4a8c2529c8cd31b6cb9770d8da6c5e07339e","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人有d 咩可以做？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1）Twitter tag @Solomon Yue, @Donald Trump, 外國Journals 話比佢地聽港共政府唔封關既決定 / 病毒輸出既後果，話比佢地知香港人都好想封關，再請求佢哋封香港出境既遊客。最好大大聲話比人知，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">柒婆係玩緊生化武器。</span></span></strong><br />\n2）本地文宣"},{"pid":"31f0ebb746171a15ef557c73e940f92fdd3cc50b","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0015d9efb54e31890ca1e39a2583c1ebdbeb0e0d","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5451ba7f91ed12b7c246a9c302b47e8cd4958698","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e95acc9c10c2ef9a22e197d4c2bb288cdad308f9","tid":1845023,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}